      <hr><a name="skip_menu"></a><h1>526 - Study Program Information Note (R)</h1>
      <hr>
      <div class="formatname">MARC 21 Bibliographic - Full</div>
      <div class="datename">October 2003</div>
      <hr>
      <table width="100%">
         <tr vAlign="top">
            <td width="45%"><strong>First Indicator</strong><br><em>Display constant controller</em><br>0 - Reading program <br>8 - No display constant generated <br><br></td>
            <td width="45%"><strong>Second Indicator</strong><br><em>Undefined</em><br># - Undefined <br><br></td>
         </tr>
      </table>
      <hr>
      <table width="100%">
         <tr vAlign="top">
            <td valign="top" width="50%" align="left"></td>
            <td valign="top" width="50%" align="left"></td>
         </tr>
         <tr vAlign="top">
            <td colspan="2"><strong>Subfield Codes</strong><br></td>
         </tr>
         <tr vAlign="top">
            <td colspan="1">$a - Program name (NR) <br>$b - Interest level (NR) <br>$c - Reading level (NR) <br>$d - Title point value (NR) <br>$i - Display text (NR) <br></td>
            <td colspan="1">$x - Nonpublic note (R) <br>$z - Public note (R) <br>$5 - Institution to which field applies (NR) <br>$6 - Linkage (NR) <br>$8 - Field link and sequence number (R) <br></td>
         </tr>
   </table>
      <hr>
      <h3>FIELD DEFINITION AND SCOPE</h3>
      <p>Note giving the name of a study program which uses the title described in the record.
         Details about the study program data elements are also contained in the field. Field 526
         is generally used for formal curriculum-based study or reading programs.      </p>
      <hr>
      <h3>GUIDELINES FOR APPLYING CONTENT DESIGNATORS</h3>
      <h4><span class="box">&#9632;</span> INDICATORS
      </h4>
      <div class="indicator"><strong>First Indicator - Display constant controller</strong> <div class="description">Controls the generation of a display constant preceding the note.
            <div class="indicatorvalue"><strong>0 - Reading program</strong> <div class="description">Used to generate the display constant <em>Reading program:</em>.
               </div>
            </div>
            <div class="indicatorvalue"><strong>8 - No display constant generated</strong> <div class="description">Information may be provided in subfield $i (Display text) when
                                       special introductory text is needed.
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="indicator"><strong>Second Indicator - Undefined</strong> <div class="description">Undefined and contains a blank (#).
            </div>
      </div>
      <h4><span class="box">&#9632;</span> SUBFIELD CODES
      </h4>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$a - Program name</strong> <div class="description">Name of the study program which uses the title described in the record.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$b - Interest level</strong> <div class="description">Interest level of the title as assigned by the study program entered in subfield
                              $a.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$c - Reading level</strong> <div class="description">Reading level of the title as assigned by the study program entered in subfield
                              $a.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$d - Title point value</strong> <div class="description">Title point value of the title as assigned by the study program entered in
                              $a.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$i - Display text</strong> <div class="description">Text intended to be displayed preceding the other data contained in the field.</div>
         <div class="example">
            <table width="100%">
               <tr>
                  <td valign="top" width="5%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="15%" align="left"></td>
               </tr>
               <tr>
                  <td vAlign="top" colspan="1" align="left"><strong>526</strong></td>
                  <td vAlign="top" colspan="9" align="left"><strong>8#</strong><strong>$i</strong>January 1999 selection for:<strong>$a</strong>Happy Valley Reading Club.
                  </td>
               </tr>
            </table>
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$x - Nonpublic note</strong> <div class="description">Note pertaining to the study program that is not displayed to the public.</div>
         <div class="example">
            <table width="100%">
               <tr>
                  <td valign="top" width="5%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="15%" align="left"></td>
               </tr>
               <tr>
                  <td vAlign="top" colspan="1" align="left"><strong>526</strong></td>
                  <td vAlign="top" colspan="9" align="left"><strong>0#</strong><strong>$a</strong>Accelerated Reader AR<strong>$b</strong>Upper Grades<strong>$c</strong>6.4<strong>$d</strong>7.0<strong>$x</strong>This item used for a special parent's
                                          viewing.
                  </td>
               </tr>
            </table>
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$z - Public note</strong> <div class="description">Note pertaining to the study program that is displayed to the public.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$5 - Institution to which field applies</strong> <div class="description">See description of this subfield in Appendix A: <em><a href="http://www.loc.gov/marc/bibliographic/ecbdcntf.html">Control
                                       Subfields</a></em>.
         </div>
         <div class="example">
